            Real-time emotion recognition
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            Biometric response tracking
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Mixed Reality Integration</h3>
        <img src="https://pixabay.com/get/g47339ab83954868a7ec2af96360f25998a79be1e85b4b2c4a6ceb1724f63b0c1bb06a218ec9a52264b9b9d4462d6cfc2848945e61e35c81818bf4b7f175c2a30_1280.jpg" alt="Mixed Reality" class="rounded-lg mb-4 w-full h-48 object-cover" />
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            Holographic AR campaigns (22% traffic increase)
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            Virtual try-on solutions
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            Immersive brand experiences
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Decentralized AI</h3>
        <img src="https://pixabay.com/get/g00d6a4b947a335466e2811d0d0d0f212640c00b3c87b6121f7c87c86d70d8231ebb0ca929ece111049648ac5b645472d5fada452338873988bf9dc047865ad22_1280.jpg" alt="Decentralized AI" class="rounded-lg mb-4 w-full h-48 object-cover" />
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            AI marketplaces reducing costs by 41%
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            Blockchain-verified ad delivery
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-primary mr-2">→</span>
            Community-trained marketing models
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Industry Impact Section -->
  <Section background="gray">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">Industry-Specific Impact</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">How AI is transforming marketing across different sectors</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">B2B Tech</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Complex sales cycle optimization, account-based marketing automation, and predictive lead scoring are revolutionizing how tech companies approach marketing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">E-commerce</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Dynamic pricing optimization, visual search integration, and inventory prediction are creating more efficient and personalized shopping experiences.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Finance</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Risk-aware marketing automation, compliance-first content generation, and personalized financial product recommendations are transforming customer engagement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Retail</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">In-store behavior analysis, smart shelf technology, and unified online-offline experiences are creating seamless customer journeys.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">AI Adoption by Industry</h3>
          <div class="aspect-square rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-white p-4">
            <canvas id="industryAdoptionChart"></canvas>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary mb-4">Success Metrics</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Engagement</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li>→ 28% higher engagement rates (Salesforce, 2024)</li>
                <li>→ 34% faster response times (Martech.org, 2025)</li>
                <li>→ 40% increase in qualified leads (McKinsey, 2024)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-secondary/10 rounded-lg p-4">
              <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Efficiency</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700">
                <li>→ 60% reduced content costs (Deloitte, 2024)</li>
                <li>→ 61% lower support costs (Forrester Research, 2023)</li>
                <li>→ 70% less management time (Harvard Business Review, 2024)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Implementation Roadmap Section -->
  <Section background="white">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="heading-lg mb-4">Implementation Roadmap</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">Strategic phases for adopting AI in marketing</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="card">
